Since Diana is three years younger than Eduardo and Diana is already 14, then Eduardo is 14 + 3 = <<14+3=17>>17 years old.
Eduardo is four years older than Chad so Chad is 17 - 4 = <<17-4=13>>13 years old.
Faye is three years older than Chad, so Faye is 13 + 3 = <<13+3=16>>16. Answer: \boxed{16}.
